com.aerospike.helper.query

Class QueryEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aerospike.helper.query.QueryEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class QueryEngine
extends Object
implements Closeable
    This class provides a multi-filter query engine that augments the query capability in Aerospike. To achieve this the class uses a UserDefined Function written in Lua to provide the additional filtering. This UDF module packaged in the JAR and is automatically registered with the cluster.
    Author:
    peter
